<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span style="color:#006d98">غَضُّ:</span> الطرف.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وغضٌّ:</span> طري.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>